    step 2: make a function to count the leftmostsetbit in a number coz this will tell us to shift the number to the left as new numbers are comming to add
    step 3: now add the number in the shifted value
    12 will be like
    1 -> "1"
    2 ->" 10 " so ans = (1<<2) + 2
    3-> "11" so ans =  (ans <<2) + 3
    and so on


