            the approach is pretty simple but all the matter is the way in which we can do it so the it will be very efficient in terms of time complexity

       -> So we need to interate from 1 to given n and concatenate all binary string from 1 to n and return the result
       -> The result can be pretty big as n can be 1<n<10^5  which an int cant hold so wee are using long annd make sure to do mod with 10^9+7 to get the value for bigger n values

       -> Now convert the number to binary string and find it length 

         general approach                     |             binary operation
