   1.String bs=Integer.to binaryString(n);    |    1.if (n&(n-1)) ==0   len++;
     int len=bs.length()                      |      ex:- for 4-> (4 & 3) -> (100&011)==0 so len++

      -> Now append the number(binary string) to the previous binary string.

       general approach                       |             binary operation
